Description: Modern glass-style budget tracking web application
 Glass Budget is a modern budgeting tool built with Flask backend
 and glassmorphism UI design. Features include:
 .
  * User authentication and management
  * Account management (checking, savings, credit, investment)
  * Transaction tracking (income/expense)
  * Recurring bill management
  * Savings goals tracking
  * Modern glassmorphism UI design
  * Responsive design for mobile and desktop
 .
 This package includes the complete web application, systemd service
 files, and nginx configuration for production deployment on Ubuntu Server.